- 150 gr of black rice
- one carrot
- one zucchine
- 4 small mushrooms or 1 big mushroom
- Mix of seafood 250 gr
- ginger
- olive oil
- peper
- salt

1. Cut the carrots in small squares
2. Cut the zucchine in slices
3. cut the mashrooms as you wish
4. Put water in the fire and wait until it boils. Once it boils, put the black rice for 12 minutes. Once it is done, drain them and reserve.
5. In a pan, put the olive oil and wait until hot. Once it is hot, put the veggies and stir.
6. When the veggies are done, add the seafood (if the seafood is frozen, 4 minutes it is fine. If not, cook them) and flavour everything with ginger, peper, salt and whatever else you want.
7. Once eveything is cooked, lower the fire and add the rice and stir everything.
8. done.
                                               
                                               
